title: Young researcher wins 3rd Corinna Seith award (University of Bristol)
text: ( Source : University of Bristol ) Dr Alison Gregory from the University 's Centre for Academic Primary Care is joint winner of the 2015 Corinna Seith Award , run by Women Against Violence Europe ( WAVE ). Dr Gregory won the award for her paper,
